msgid "Plugin Loading"
msgstr ""

# 7a5fdae5643545ae9441254e62803417
#: ../../developer-guide/plugins/getting-started/index.en.rst:161
msgid ""
"When Traffic Server is first started, it consults the ``plugin.config`` "
"file to determine the names of all shared plugin libraries that need to "
"be loaded. The ``plugin.config`` file also defines arguments that are to "
"be passed to each plugin's initialization function, ``TSPluginInit``. The"
" :file:`records.config` file defines the path to each plugin shared "
"library, as described in :ref:`specify-the-plugins-location`."
msgstr ""

# 6f655249de144edd85374857cd210776
#: ../../developer-guide/plugins/getting-started/index.en.rst:168
msgid ""
"The path for each of these files is *<root_dir>*\\ ``/config/``, where "
"*<root_dir>* is where you installed Traffic Server."
msgstr ""

